{
  "stem": "812.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Another very important incident which I had forgotten to bring out was the fact that I had mentioned earlier that we were in Bergen-Belsen actually because we were to be exchanged for a group of Germans in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The time had come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I believe it was [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] sometime in-- in '45, may have been [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] February or March of '45, or maybe it was earlier.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A few hundred of us were taken out of our section of Bergen-Belsen in camp and put into another area of camp, because it was time for us to be exchanged for a group in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We knew it was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We thought, we hoped, we prayed it was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were, of course, overjoyed that the time had come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we were then in this section, another section, and we were told to get our belongings together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they would prepare us psychologically and so on and so forth to be exchanged and moved to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] When we got to that area of the camp, we were all standing and names were called off.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Our name was Blumenthal, started with a B.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The commandant started calling the names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He went through the A's.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He went through the B's, the C's, and alphabet was completed, and our name was not on the list.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We thought maybe at the very end, there-- he maybe made a mistake and left names out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was not on the list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My father-- we were, at that point, all together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The four of us were together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My father [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] walked up ahead and knew very well that this is not the thing to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
